{
  "stem": "3820.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I came back a couple of weeks later, my hair had not been combed for the two weeks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had to cut it all off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And things got a little easier on the farm at that point.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had stopped the searches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I thought that I would probably be there forever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, children don't really think too far ahead, I guess.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But on one of her trips into the forest, Anna fell into one of those underground houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish family hiding there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were from the ghetto that I had been in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she told them that they were welcome to come every now and then into the house when they were sure that there was no one around.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You must understand that we're talking about a little house surrounded by forests.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was hard even to see the next farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was like a-- a half a day's or more ride away, so that in the dark, it was possible to come.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they did and-- several times, to sit in a house for a little while and have hot tea and some food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She-- they saw me and I saw them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there was no acknowledgement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But it must have been fate that they did, because they ran into my uncle Sana, who survived as a partisan and was in Kiev at the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they had ended up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They asked him if he had me with him, and he said he didn't know where I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they brought him to the farm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'm a little bit ahead of myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
